                     for IPR Trust," <a href="./rfc4371">RFC 4371</a>, January 2006.

   [<a name="ref-IETF_Trust_Agmt" id="ref-IETF_Trust_Agmt">IETF_Trust_Agmt</a>] www.ietf.org/trust/IETFtrustAgreement20051208.pdf

